def to_html(style="") html = @groups.map do |group| [ "

#{group['title']}

", "
    ", flatten_subgroups(group["items"]).map {|g| "
  • #{g['title']}
    • " }, "
", ] end.flatten.join("\n") return <<-EOHTML
#{html}
EOHTML end
